title: Mermaid Dreams: An Art Collection by Selina Fenech
description: Satin scales, silky tails, mermaids of the ocean deep and others that call the sea their home. A soft cover collection of Selina Fenech's mermaid themed artworks. Includes lush, full page reprints of Fenech's artworks, sketchbook images, plus information and insight into the creation of each work. 60 pages.
author: Selina Fenech
